
What is Prisma?
Prisma is an ORM (Object Relational Mapper)
Connects your code → database
Lets you query DB using code (not raw SQL)
Generates type-safe queries

step to use prisma --
1) npm install prisma @prisma/client
2) npx prisma init
3) Add DATABASE_URL in .env
4) Define schema
5) npx prisma generate
6) npx prisma migrate dev --name init



easy way -- 
1)npx prisma init
2)npx prisma migrate dev
3) npx prisma generate
